OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBBC show is a 'lifeline'   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffor Afghan girls, UN says  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A BBC programme for children barred    
OL,6, from schools in Afghanistan has been   
OL,7, described as a "learning lifeline" by  
OL,8, the United Nations.                    
OL,10,FThe show is being used in secret school
OL,11,Flessons, the BBC has learned.          
OL,13,FIts name, Dars, means lesson in        
OL,14,FAfghanistan's official languages of    
OL,15,FDari and Pashto.                       
OL,17,FThe ruling Taliban prohibits girls from
OL,18,Freceiving secondary or higher          
OL,19,Feducation.                             
